games.comment: Brandon Marshall came within 2 receptions of tying Terrell Owens' single-game NFL record of 20 catches. Marshall caught 18 balls for 166 yards and a touchdown. At haltime, he had 10 receptions and 117 yards.    Both Cutler and
Brandon Marshall (ankle) and Dwayne Harris (foot) all going out prior to Beckham getting injured.
